FBIS4-28932 "dreas115_c_94011" FBIS-EAS-94-115 Daily Report 12 Jun 1994 North Korea Atomic Energy Department Letter Distributed at UN Atomic Energy Department Letter Distributed at UN SK1206101994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0812 GMT 12 Jun 94 SK1206101994 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 12 (KCNA) -- The letter sent by the general director of the General Department of the Atomic Energy of the DPRK to the general director of the International Atomic Energy Agency regarding the latter's hurried "conclusion" that the agency could not guarantee the non-diversion of nuclear material, alleging that the technical possibility for later measurement of core fuel rods was lost at the 5-megawatt experimental nuclear power plant of the DPRK, was distributed as official document of the UN Security Council S/1994/677 on June 6.
